warezcdn.title: DNA²: Dokokade nakushita aitsu no aitsu

imdb.title: DNA²: Dokokade nakushita aitsu no aitsu
imdb.plot: A female time traveler must work with a teenage boy who is in danger of becoming a future menace because of her interference.

episodes.title: Mirai kara no shôjo: Karin
episodes.plot: Sometime in the future, overpopulation is a serious problem, thanks to the "Mega-Playboy" who passed his playboy DNA on to his one hundred children, who in turn had one hundred children each, and so on! Karin Aoi, a DNA Operator, has traveled back in time in order to stop the original, but is Junta Momonari really him? He can't even look at a girl without throwing up!

episodes.title: Megapure tanjô! Junta
episodes.plot: Junta is delighted that he can now talk to a girl normally and has already charmed Tomoko with his Mega-playboy power.

episodes.title: Matsuri no yoru ni Ami
episodes.plot: Junta's Mega-Playboy DNA hasn't stabilized yet. One minute he's suave, and the next he's struggling not to puke on a girl's shoes. Before the DNA can take hold fully, Karin launches a plan involving Junta's childhood friend, Ami. Could it be that the Mega-Playboy's charm doesn't work on everyone?

episodes.title: Nekkuresu wa dare ni? Ami
episodes.plot: When Junta asks Ami about what type of present he should get a girl he likes, she tells him to get a necklace.

episodes.title: Dare ni mo ienai! Kotomi
episodes.plot: Kotomi tells her friend Ami that she's lovesick.

episodes.title: Junta wa Kotomi ni nani o shita?
episodes.plot: Ami runs after Kotomi and is tracked by Junta and Karin.

episodes.title: Watashi nosubete o agetai no!
episodes.plot: Kotomi is still interested in Junta. Ami tells Karin that Junta has to date Kotomi now that she's told him her feelings.

episodes.title: Zutto anata ga zoba ni ita
episodes.plot: Mega-Playboy Junta tells Kotomi that she doesn't have to change and that she's fine just the way she is.

episodes.title: Sono dangan wa Ryûji no mune ni...
episodes.plot: Karin's boss, Yokomori, warns her that they've run out of budget and this is the last bullet she'll get.

episodes.title: Abunai Ryûji no abunai nôryoku
episodes.plot: As a result of being shot with DCM bullet Ryuji has gained the power to absorb other people DNA and morph into them.

episodes.title: Megapure ni natcha dame!!
episodes.plot: Junta believes the only way he can defeat Ryuji is by transforming into Mega-Playboy. Karin is opposed to it because the change might be permanent.

episodes.title: Bai bai megapurei-bôi
episodes.plot: The only one who can stop Ryuji is the Mega-Playboy. But can Junta risk unleashing him again?
